{"tid":1508201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣開槍文宣方向建議","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:01:43.000Z","uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c94d249365dfb9c65f264f46dba248d5cd12586","tid":1508201,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"1.危險使用槍械/意圖射擊記者<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/26/201902_07e5a2614478389e3b223ec7b5c9bf9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F201902_07e5a2614478389e3b223ec7b5c9bf9a.png&h=6dfb6da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖可見牠將手指放於板機上，加上牠們多次將槍枝指向記者，違反以下安全守則2、3條：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqTMt4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqTMt4q.png&h=a511545f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource：香港童軍總會 <a href=\"https://www.scout.org.hk/supplement/chi/su/interestgroups/stsc/NSP.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scout.org.hk%2Fsupplement%2Fchi%2Fsu%2Finterestgroups%2Fstsc%2FNSP.htm&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=e1c2218a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scout.org.hk/supplement/chi/su/interestgroups/stsc/NSP.htm</a><br />\n因此有理由相信牠們不能正確使用槍械及意圖射擊記者<br />\n<br />\n2.向天開槍<br />\n向天開槍可能擊中無辜市民，亦違反守則<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2007年5月，澳門發生警員向天鳴槍事件，時任香港警察員佐級協會主席鍾錦華曾向傳媒表示，香港人口稠密，向天開槍有潛在危險，流彈易傷及途人，因此警例對警務人員使用槍械有嚴格規定，並且不容許人員以向天開槍作為示警方法。</span></strong><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160811/s00001/1470920650164/【旺角大衝突】向天開槍交警獲嘉許-民陣譴責獎勵疑違例警-批獎罰不公\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160811%2Fs00001%2F1470920650164%2F%E3%80%90%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E3%80%91%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E7%8D%B2%E5%98%89%E8%A8%B1-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E7%8D%8E%E5%8B%B5%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B%E8%AD%A6-%E6%89%B9%E7%8D%8E%E7%BD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=4f70aec6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160811%2Fs00001%2F1470920650164%2F%E3%80%90%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E3%80%91%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E7%8D%B2%E5%98%89%E8%A8%B1-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E7%8D%8E%E5%8B%B5%E7%96%91%E9%81%95%E4%BE%8B%E8%AD%A6-%E6%89%B9%E7%8D%8E%E7%BD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC&h=acef8e1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160811/s00001/1470920650164/【旺角大衝突】向天開槍交警獲嘉許-民陣譴責獎勵疑違例警-批獎罰不公</a><br />\n<br />\n3.不當使用武力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWuzC0v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWuzC0v.gif&h=2c4e0d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不過，有前警務人員向本報質疑，有關警員開槍情況跟學堂訓練有別，甚至不諱言「警員學嘅安全防禦法應該拎咗去墊煲」。他解釋，根據警察學院訓練，警員絕對可以先使用警棍及胡椒噴劑，「人哋拎刀先拔槍」。至於一名手無寸鐵市民跪在地上，換來被警員一腳踢跌，該前警員慨嘆：「收番埋支槍抬人埋一邊真係咁難？」</span></strong><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190826/20756277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20756277&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a8c48a48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20756277&h=76d2e1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190826/20756277</a><br />\n<br />\n就算d片cut 咗頭，以上三點都係核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68614eb226816c63a085bbae3ec4037ac6019599","tid":1508201,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"求各位巴絲幫手推post"},{"pid":"e4230ab46e18709cae475a7e770ea2f34e10fcc6","tid":1508201,"uid":33